PEOPLE ex rel. HICKSON, Appellant, MOSS et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. December 8, 1899.) Proceedings by the people, on the r lotion of William Hickson, against Frank Mo and others. F. B. House, for appellant. Farley, for respondents.

No opinion. Writ missed, with costs.
